@startuml
title SimulDIESEL - Communication Stack (Arquitetura)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "Host Local (WinForms)" {
  [WinForms UI]
  [FrmBpmLogic]
  [FrmGsaLogic]
  [BpmSerialService.Shared\n(acesso global transitório)]
  [BpmSerialService]
  [BpmClient]
  [GsaClient]
  [SdhClient]
  [SdgwSession]
  [SdGwTxScheduler\nHigh / Normal / Low]
  [SdGwLinkEngine]
  [SdGwLinkSupervisor\nsilêncio -> ping Low]
  [SerialTransport]

  [WinForms UI] --> [FrmBpmLogic]
  [WinForms UI] --> [FrmGsaLogic]
  [FrmBpmLogic] --> [BpmSerialService.Shared\n(acesso global transitório)]
  [FrmGsaLogic] --> [BpmSerialService.Shared\n(acesso global transitório)]
  [BpmSerialService.Shared\n(acesso global transitório)] --> [BpmSerialService]
  [BpmSerialService] --> [BpmClient]
  [BpmSerialService] --> [GsaClient]
  [BpmSerialService] --> [SdGwLinkSupervisor\nsilêncio -> ping Low]
  [BpmClient] --> [SdhClient] : funcional High
  [GsaClient] --> [SdhClient] : funcional High
  [SdhClient] --> [SdgwSession]
  [SdgwSession] --> [SdGwTxScheduler\nHigh / Normal / Low]
  [SdGwLinkSupervisor\nsilêncio -> ping Low] --> [SdGwTxScheduler\nHigh / Normal / Low] : ping Low
  [SdGwTxScheduler\nHigh / Normal / Low] --> [SdGwLinkEngine]
  [SdGwLinkEngine] --> [SerialTransport]
  [SdGwLinkEngine] --> [SdGwLinkSupervisor\nsilêncio -> ping Low] : ValidFrameReceived
}

package "BPM Gateway" {
  [Handshake textual inicial]
  [SggwLink\nSDGW binário\nkeepalive por frame válido\natividade = 4000 ms]
  [GatewayApp]
  [GwRouter\ntimeout = 100 ms]
  [BPM.local]

  [Handshake textual inicial] --> [SggwLink\nSDGW binário\nkeepalive por frame válido\natividade = 4000 ms]
  [SggwLink\nSDGW binário\nkeepalive por frame válido\natividade = 4000 ms] --> [GatewayApp]
  [GatewayApp] --> [BPM.local]
  [GatewayApp] --> [GwRouter\ntimeout = 100 ms]
}

package "GSA" {
  [GSA TLV/I2C]
  [LED_BUILTIN]
  [GSA TLV/I2C] --> [LED_BUILTIN]
}

[SerialTransport] --> [Handshake textual inicial] : bootstrap
[SerialTransport] --> [SggwLink\nSDGW binário\nkeepalive por frame válido\natividade = 4000 ms] : RX/TX SDGW
[GwRouter\ntimeout = 100 ms] --> [GSA TLV/I2C]

note bottom of [BpmSerialService]
Após o primeiro Linked, RX SDGW binário
continua sendo entregue ao engine
mesmo se o estado lógico cair
temporariamente para LinkFailed,
desde que a porta continue aberta.
end note

note bottom of [SdGwTxScheduler\nHigh / Normal / Low]
Busy deixa de ser o mecanismo principal
de arbitragem entre tráfego funcional
e ping de supervisão.
end note
@enduml
